    "through only generating a kind of image using a generic prompt like 'banana', or exhibiting high degrees of directness using targeted prompts.Second, like users, GenAI systems can make less or more relevant and non-redundant contributions.",
    "But they can only exhibit a certain degree of independence and cannot demonstrate leadership, for lack of intentions.",
    "However, if unchallenged by a user, they will exercise control in producing certain images rather than others, given a prompt.",
